---------------------------------------------------

Wooden Sen'SeY is an action-platformer for  PC  and
Mac, set in a unique "Japan Steam  Rock"  universe.
You follow Goro,  a  village  chief,  as  he  seeks
revenge through a variety of levels. He will defeat
his enemies using his axes to slice,  dice,  squash
and grapple! Upper Byte, the  French  indie  studio
behind Wooden Sen'SeY, is a tiny team with only two
members: Cedric, the creative force,  and  Camille,
the insane coder.  Their  ultimate  goal  is  world
domination. But for now, nice polished games,  with
hardcore old school gameplay and nice  graphics  is
enough!
